⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Captain Rolfe
node M1 · M1 · ⟦Captain Rolfe:M1:4347fc⟧

WHO   — Captain Rolfe — the Pirate Lord of Skull's Bay
WHAT  — A trafficker and crime-king of the southern waters who runs a slaving venture in partnership with Arobynn's Guild — and finds two of Arobynn's own assassins turning that bargain to ash.
WHERE — M1 · Maas  Framework inputs: Throne of Glass — The Assassin's Blade & book one  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because in Skull's Bay profit is the only law, and a Pirate Lord who shows mercy does not stay lord for long; because the map on his skin always points him toward what is worth taking.
HOW   — By the ledger and the lash, by the loyalty of a pirate fleet, and by the living chart inked across his hands that no rival can read or steal.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The map on my hands knows every coast — and every coast knows the Pirate Lord of Skull's Bay.

